Popular Nollywood actor, Lateef Adedimeji, reacts to a video of his wife, Bimpe Oyebade, and her colleague dancing in a close-up manner. In a video shared by the newly wedded actress on her page, Bimpe and her colleague, Itele, dance like lovers to a traditional romantic song. The dance that caught many as hilarious, triggered the husband, Lateef Adedimeji, who took to the comment session to react.  “Mummy , sa come and learn how to dance jeje,” Lateef wrote as he encourages wife to resume dance lessons at home. Read Also: Actor Lateef Adedimeji Shares New Pictures From A Movie Set (Photos)     A post shared by OYEBADE ADEBIMPE R. ADEDIMEJI (@mo_bimpe) 